quran[25]{c,v,t}:
  37,52,( jo ) kehta tha ke bhala tum bhi aisi baton ke bawar karne walon mein ho
  37,53,bhala jab hum mar gay aur matti aur haddiyan hogaye tokiya hum ko badla miley ga ?
  37,54,( phir ) kahe ga ke bhala tum ( usay ) jhaank kar dekhna chahtay ho ?
  37,55,( itnay mein ) woh ( khud ) jhanke ga to is ko wast dozakh mein dekhe ga
  37,56,kahe ga ke khuda ki qasam too to mujhe halaak hi krchka tha
  37,57,aur agar mere perwar-digaar ki meharbani nah hoti to mein bhi un mein hota jo ( azaab mein ) haazir kiye gay hain
  37,58,kiya ( yeh nahi ke ) hum ( aindah kabhi ) marnay ke nahi
  37,59,haan ( jo ) pehli baar marna ( tha so mrchke ) aur hamein azaab bhi nahi honay ka
  37,60,be shak yeh barri kamyabi hai
  37,61,aisi hi ( nematon ) ke liye amal karne walon ko amal karne chahiye
  37,62,bhala yeh mehmani achi hai ya تھوہر ka darakht ?
  37,63,hum ne is ko zaalmon ke liye azaab bana rakha hai
  37,64,woh aik darakht hai ke jahannum ke asfal mein ugay ga
  37,65,uss ke khoshay aisay hon ge jaisay shaitano ke sir
  37,66,so woh isi mein se khayen ge aur isi se pait bharain ge
  37,67,phir is ( khanay ) ke sath un ko garam pani mila kar diya jaye ga
  37,68,phir un ko dozakh ki taraf lotaya jaye ga
  37,69,unhon ne apne baap dada ko gumraah hi paaya
  37,70,so woh un hi ke peechay doray chalay jatay hain
  37,71,aur un se peshtar bohat se log bhi gumraah hogaye they
  37,72,aur hum ne un mein mutnabba karne walay beje
  37,73,so dekh lau ke jin ko mutnabbakiya gaya tha un ka injaam kaisa howa
  37,74,haan khuda ke bandgaan khaas ( ka injaam bohat acha howa )
  37,75,aur hum ko Nooh ne puraka so ( dekh lau ke ) hum ( dua ko kaisay ) achay qubool karne walay hain
  37,76,aur hum ne un ko aur un ke ghar walon ko barri museebat se nijaat di
